den.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 3.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aErkenntnistheorie. 4aExperiment. 4aModell. 4aPhilosophie. 4aSprache. 4aSprachphilosophie. 4aWahrnehmung. 7aPHILOSOPHY / Epistemology.2bisacsh  aEpistemology.  aLanguage.  aPhilosophy.40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839401255zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de GruyterzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839401255zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839401255/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-GOA